Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Making one plus one plus one\Nequal ten instead of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's name is Vertex.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A dreadful being that was born from a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to eliminate them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did they name them Vertex?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A word which means "the top."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I still didn't know that Vertex was blank by blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of heroes can only be used by\Ninnocent girls who were chosen by Shinjyu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to depend on you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, your next assignment is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-to rest properly for a while.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't transform unless\Nyou have a stable state of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't last until the end if you're always tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yay!\N-Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-What should we do?\N-Ines?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's part of our job to rest\Nin preparation for the next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, will I be able to relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, Nogi-sama is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy life in Kagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so plush, both your outfit and your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go out, so that we can enjoy our time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Her high energy makes me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey. Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice, nice, yeah. Yeah, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,SONOCCHI AND I ARE ON OUR WAY\NSO EARLY!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,DAAAAANG\NI'LL BE WAITING!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yay, Kagawa!\N-Gin is excited too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get into the spirit too, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, hey, yay! Yes, yes, yes!\N-Just listening to music won't get me excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you enjoying yourself?\N-Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let the fun time off begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-Enjoy!\N-Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you and start running\NTo a place where no one can catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to fulfill it\NThe promise from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki Yuna is a Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A bud of happiness in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It had a silver glow\NI'll show it to you when it blossoms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In the album that I looked back on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like that back then, and it still is now\NWe're laughing together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The season which gets colored from the south
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, say "I'm back"\NI'll definitely come to welcome you straightaway
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you and start running\NTo a place where no one can catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to fulfill it\NThe promise from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you patiently for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back\NPlease, don't ever leave me again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 3 EVERYDAY LIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't think it suits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true. Right, Wasshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I've never seen anyone bleed like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You look really good in it, Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is this feeling that's welling up within me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This Wasshi seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,like a pro. So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Photos express love. Oh, Gin,\Nyou have to try on all the beautiful clothes today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your name means silver, but this is gold.\N-I'm so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The score is high for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-This one is out of the question.\N-No, it's not, not, not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-That was good.\N-What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll look good in an outfit like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't wear such unpatriotic clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you would look great in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'm just going to make you wear it.\NCome on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice. You look good in it too, Sumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You could even become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be your first fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't wear such unpatriotic clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A Japanese woman like me, doing such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,SONOKO'S DREAM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonoko's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonocchi, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,am prepared to become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, too, Sonocchi and Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Me too?\N-That rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The concert is going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a hero-like liveliness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Were there a lot of audiences?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How rock 'n' roll of you to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you draw, Sumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the second destroyer of the\NShokaku aircraft carrier, Zuikaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a carrier vessel which participated as
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a major force in a number of battles\Nin the Showa period during the former century.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It became the decoy,\Nand did its best until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so knowledgeable about those things, Sumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a historian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as expected, you're a serious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-It does sound like a dream Wasshi would have.\N-Do you have a dream, Sonocchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a novel writer would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been posting my work online sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I kind of get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You do have a unique imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you guys to be in the novel as characters too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san who is kind and reliable,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and Wasshi who is earnest and sometimes funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than being boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be relied on too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I like your expression when\Nyou're kind of feeling sorry for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's not a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the atmosphere\Nbetween you two is great right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your dream, Gin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in kindergarten, I wanted to be\Na pretty guardian to protect my family and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. The superhero who protects the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's every girl's aspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you blush?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, families are nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought it would be nice\Nto get married and settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But that would make my dream for the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's you, Mino-san,\Nthat dream will come true right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm looking forward to seeing you dressed in white.\N-Come on, stop poking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use it as a story in my novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't. It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shall we practice...\N-A novel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-...the goodbye kiss?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonocchi's novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"SPACE SANCHO"\NRIVERS OF TEARS... A MASTERPIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She has great reviews.\NShe has the highest number of readers as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you would expect of Sonocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll influence everyone to have national defense ideology\Nthrough my historical novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's see what kind of reviews I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SENTENCES ARE LONG,\NAND IT'S PAINFUL TO READ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS AUTHOR SHOULD JUST WRITE COLUMNS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that my writing skills can't fully\Nconvey the excellence of my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wasuyu.\N-Sonoko's dream number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,SONOKO'S DREAM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My real identity is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the hero of wealth and military strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the National Defense Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a knight in shining armor\Nwho looked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a fashionable outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rock!\N-Wasuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,23 CENTIMETERS\NGRATITUDE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Orientation with the first-grade students\Nis coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Be aware that you are in sixth grade,\Nand make sure to look after them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,GRADE 6\NCLASS 2
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do in an orientation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You do fun things with the first-graders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocent first-year students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As heroes, our role is to protect this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-In other words...\N-In other words?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of our mission to look ahead\Nand educate them on patriotism.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a plan, then. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,TO NOGI SONOKO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is it a letter of challenge?\N-Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a chain letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whenever I notice, I'm always looking at you."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just as I expected. It's a duel. Where will it be?\N-It's a curse. We might need salt to purify.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"I would like to get to know you better."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That is more terrifying than\Njust placing a curse on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your job must be hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's precisely why I want to be your support."\NThat's what it says here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi, this could be...\NThe thing that starts with the letter L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-A statue of Rakan?\N-No, a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot, dot, dot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, love, love...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I got a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it as soon as I saw\Nthe handwriting and the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who gave me this is a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm back.\N-Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi-sama, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,TO SUMI WASHIO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a love letter too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE AN HONORS STUDENT, BUT\NYOU SOUND NAGGY WHEN YOU GIVE ADVICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE, BE AWARE OF IT.\NANONYMOUS SENDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I get excited about a mere piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm going to push you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're going to aim for the Ryugu castle.\N-So fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-One, two, three, four...\N-Hey, Sumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to be warming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Accidents at the pool are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do a warm-up properly,\Nyour body won't be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have this whole place to ourselves,\Nso let's enjoy ourselves freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if the enemy comes right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,does that mean we have to go\Non a mission in our swim suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that irregular probably\Ndoesn't happen that often, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one did come early.\NWe shouldn't let our guards down too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi really does have big boobs.\NMaybe she's actually in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's older. Maybe she's in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gin. Do you want to race me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun. I'll accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We have things to do for the orientation\Nafter this, so don't overdo it--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigh... Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You overdid it at the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. One final push.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to the actual day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you guys, it'll be an awesome orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The evil monster is coming\Nto attack our country from beyond the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thump, thump...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"What a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me this land."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This shameless monster is saying things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:16:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, the monster would take over this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't know what to do.\N-I'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We have Shinjyu-sama on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's gather our courage and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Alongside the National Defense Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-That paper is blank.\N-It's blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's call them all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,National Defense Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,National Defense Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,People are calling us to protect the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're screaming for us to protect love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Attention.\N-Attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-A patriotic warrior.\N-A patriotic warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-National Defense Mask arrives.\N-National Defense Mask arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,RICH COUNTRY, STRONG ARMY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll learn how\Nto defend our nation while exercising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now stand up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is clear today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll now begin the national defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to bump into each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,NATIONAL DEFENSE EXERCISE\NSONG BY SUMI WASHIO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A round, full, bright, red sun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To the right, to the right\NRound and round
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up to the sky\NSay hello
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look down and say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Clench your fists\NUp, up, and up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To the front, to the back\NUp, up, and up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Both feet firmly on the ground\NThrough and through
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With all your might\NJump, jump, jump
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a deep breath\NPush, push, push
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide your presence\NSlowly, slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is another peaceful day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:18:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rich country, strong army!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,SONOKO'S DREAM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonoko's dream number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As punishment for brainwashing\Nthe students in the lower grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I forbid you from eating udon for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-I can't eat udon anymore!\N-Oh, no. We should go to the hospital right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's over!\N-Calm down, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. But, Sumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take too much of the housekeeper's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel calmer when I'm doing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's Sunday, why don't you go\Nand play with Nogi-san and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gin has plans, so we're on our own today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should go and do what you like, Sumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking Gin might get in touch\Nto ask me to hang out with her after her plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sonocchi might suddenly\Ncome to the house like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you made good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,GIN: I'M SHOPPING WITH MY\NFAMILY NEAR THE STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,SONOKO: I'M WALKING AROUND THAT AREA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,SUMI: SONOCCHI, SHOUT YOUR NAME\NREPEATEDLY IF YOU GET LOST
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,SONOKO: SONOKO NOGI\NSONOKO: SONOKO NOGI
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, we all got together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Heroes naturally get drawn towards each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I'm glad Gin found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay that we haven't\Nsaid hi to your family, Mino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. You already know\Nmy dad and my mom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not good at those kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice that you go out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-...to shop with your family on your day off.\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's embarrassing when\Nyou bump into someone you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with my errands,\Nso I'll hang out with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, little bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be sad because your sister is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Our time off is almost coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be on alert again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We should brace ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The orientation ended up like that, but it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It went by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, you guys are going\Nin a different direction than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our time off is going to end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you thought, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I said that I was confident\Nabout being able to rest, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because of our job, I wasn't sure\Nif I could actually relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was an unnecessary worry\Nwith the three of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, right, Wasshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Her face says yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If Vertex destroys Shinjyu-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,this fun everyday life will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-We'll never let that happen, right?\N-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go home if we stay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Disperse.\N-I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just have a sleepover.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-That sounds great. Let's do it at Gin's house.\N-My place? I have two younger brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,ON THE NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.03,0:24:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-Heroes possess courage and determination.\N-What? Two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is this?\N-He shot an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.87,0:24:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just as you'd expect of Sonocchi.\N-Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE\NSOUL
